  "synopsis": "The idol unit \"B-PROJECT\" has successfully completed their second JAPAN Dome live concert, and changes are afoot at the major record company \"Gandara Music.\"\n\nTsubasa Sumisora, who works as an A&amp;R, will now oversee not only \"KitaKore,\" \"THRIVE,\" \"MooNs,\" and \"KiLLER KiNG\" but also a new artist from a different genre named \"Ultras.\"\n\nThe synergy created from the meeting of B-PROJECT and Ultras is now resonating with a thrilling and passionate \"love call\"!\n\n(Source: Crunchyroll)",
